## BrowserJsPlumbInstance.removeFromDragGroup() method

Removes the given element(s) from any drag group they may be in. You don't need to supply the drag group id, as elements can only be in one drag group anyway.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
removeFromDragGroup(...els: Array<Element>): void;
```

## Parameters

|  Parameter | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  els | Array&lt;Element&gt; | Elements to remove from drag groups. |

<b>Returns:</b>

void
